ry': {'value': 'Bluepearl Stone Oak small animal rotating internship offers an outstanding opportunity for highly motivated, hardworking and professional individuals to learn in a busy and friendly referral hospital. 

Through 2 week rotations, interns work under the direct supervision of board-certified clinicians and residents in Surgery, Internal Medicine, Neurology, Critical Care and Emergency. Cardiology is part-time. On emergency, rotating interns work alongside experienced ER doctors during daytime and overnight rotations. Out rotations can be used for other specialties. 

