none', 'matchedWords': []}, 'summary': {'value': 'Bulger Veterinary Hospital is seeking candidates for 6 rotating small animal internships, with a focus on primary case management in general practice,  ER,  and surgery. This will be our seventh year offering a rotating internship, having started the program in June 2020.

